metadata.name: 001A - Gabriella, Holy Sister
metadata.description:
Rarity : Epic

Gabriella is a kind and pure angel.
In the human world, as a nun, her mission is to spread faith in the hearts of humans to strengthen her father's power on Earth.

Quote : 
"It's time to pray my child, confess your sins so that our father can forgive you and give you the strength to move forward"

- Gabriella
